UK: UK money market forecasts 700 mln stg shortage.UK money market forecasts 700 mln stg shortage.The average of forecasts by UK money market brokers of today's market shortage is 700 million stg, according to a Reuter market survey.The official forecast for the shortage will be released by the Bank of England at between 0845 GMT and 0900 GMT.-- London Newsroom +44 171 542 5109